{"tid":1497942,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[香港人抗爭時間線]想整個時間線網站","createTime":"2019-08-23T07:55:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T09:37:19.000Z","uid":180125,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"fb5b57df814d7f103e7473c0292e8d42ac9c089a","tid":1497942,"uid":180125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T07:55:02.000Z","msg":"基於香港人實在太忙，雖然應付事情太多，有見及此想整個時間線網站方便隨時喚醒大家同向國際宣揚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n暫時重係構思階級，想收集意見睇下可行性 <br />\n暫時未諗住成立團隊，因為初步構思用簡單工具去完成個綱站<br />\n如果支持佔大多數就會根隨以下步驟<br />\n<br />\n現階段計劃：<br />\n1. 收集意見<br />\n----如確定實行----<br />\n1. 討論方案<br />\n2. 設定名稱/網址/Logo<br />\n3. 註冊網站<br />\n2. 收集圖片及資料<br />\n3. 處理文檔<br />\n4. 製作網站<br />\n5. 正式推出<br />\n<br />\n唔知大家點睇，歡迎討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00fbf614ea54db69d91a9b0b7045b8b7b5d0a531","tid":1497942,"uid":180125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T07:55:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSeIe_KlTkz0blOduE47yIpawZSWK8vMKfybRkdQGCc85JLEIg/viewform?usp=sf_link\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSeIe_KlTkz0blOduE47yIpawZSWK8vMKfybRkdQGCc85JLEIg%2Fviewform%3Fusp%3Dsf_link&d=d0UHt22HnArKS4Vgrvpv1Rdm8TOyDCEw47gAfDhO9KY%3D&h=2cf2db73\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSeIe_KlTkz0blOduE47yIpawZSWK8vMKfybRkdQGCc85JLEIg/viewform?usp=sf_link</a><br />\n<br />\n補翻條Link"},{"pid":"703a6a51ce99503bd74c4c95789215deffddd2ef","tid":1497942,"uid":180125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T07:57:18.000Z","msg":"構思上網站有以下內容：<br />\n1. 時間線<br />\n2. 活動日程<br />\n3. 重點新聞"},{"pid":"466c16e162aac1d67d4654baf8f5a23a342f9eef","tid":1497942,"uid":84308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T07:58:12.000Z","msg":"警方已向 824「燃點香港&middot;全民覺醒」觀塘遊行集會活動發出不反對通知書<br />\n<br />\n路線為：駿業街遊樂場&gt;駿業街&gt;海濱道&gt;順業街&gt;偉業街&gt;常怡道&gt;宏照道&gt;零碳天地外<br />\n<br />\n詳情將會稍後透過KT tg channel 發放：<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">「燃點香港&middot;全民覺醒」</div></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">五大訴求、缺一不可</div></strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">智能燈柱、侵犯私穩</div></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>日期：24/8/2019<br />\n時間：1300集會、1330遊行、1600解散<br />\n集會地點：駿業街遊樂場<br />\n遊行起點：駿業街遊樂場</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n公海： <a href=\"http://t.me/kt824discuss\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fkt824discuss&d=d0UHt22HnArKS4Vgrvpv1Rdm8TOyDCEw47gAfDhO9KY%3D&h=5320f416\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/kt824discuss</a><br />\n<br />\n資料發佈： <a href=\"http://t.me/kt824info\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fkt824info&d=d0UHt22HnArKS4Vgrvpv1Rdm8TOyDCEw47gAfDhO9KY%3D&h=6b5f9722\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/kt824info</a><br />\n<br />\n文宣： <a href=\"http://t.me/kt824promo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fkt824promo&d=d0UHt22HnArKS4Vgrvpv1Rdm8TOyDCEw47gAfDhO9KY%3D&h=389c20e1\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/kt824promo</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qbBYwct.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqbBYwct.jpg&h=cabbffda&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a9ac49ddb98342a91e9c31d87f4df8cc87b47d86","tid":1497942,"uid":262389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T07:59:02.000Z","msg":"「千字文」毋忘初衷，我「反思」故我在<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1497022\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1497022</a>"},{"pid":"308a835d06f3b272248a67048113e0d6c545e922","tid":1497942,"uid":180125,"like"